libbpf: libbpf (library for loading eBPF programs and accessing eBPF objects)
libbpf:
libbpf: libbpf is a C-based library containing a BPF loader that takes
libbpf: compiled BPF object files and prepares and loads them into the Linux
libbpf: kernel. libbpf takes the heavy lifting of loading, verifying
libbpf: and attaching BPF programs to various kernel hooks, allowing BPF
libbpf: application developers to focus only on BPF program correctness
libbpf: and performance.
